<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>After <a href="https://spring.io/blog/2015/12/17/spring-framework-4-2-4-4-1-9-released">4.2.4 and 4.1.9 earlier today</a>, it is my pleasure to announce that Spring Framework <a href="https://jira.spring.io/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10000&amp;version=15402">3.2.16 is now available</a>.</p>
